==Text==
A long list, recording the "names" you once encountered or heard of in Amphoreus.<br />
''They are not merely data from the countless extrapolations of Scepter δ-me13, drawn from the simulated world of Amphoreus. Because of your arrival, they changed their fates, lived as though real, and remain as memories etched in your mind.''<br />
